						               													<description>Entities is a 2-in-1 board game including the best of cooperative, competitive, and single player modes in a world where the chances of survival are slim to none. Adversaries from different parts of this plane will have the mission to save their own lives only by facing the Entities: beings created by the Demiurge with the sole purpose of destroying the human race and giving rise to a new world.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Four contenders heeded the call of the mysterious Demiurge, who summoned them to the Magnetic Mount to be the only survivors of their era, but there will be only one conquering the Mount.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In order to reach the exit, you must complete your Quest Board and get three Treasures from the Entities you defeat. But not so fast! You must cross the Portal with enough energy to defeat Greiden, Guardian of the Path, so you will have to get the necessary equipment and experience from the Blue and Red decks.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Along the way, you have to watch out for the Demiurge, who will be constantly attacking the area and you will have to be cunning to avoid him between the enemy attacks and Entities hunting.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If your strength falters you can head to the Vimana, the Ship of the Gods, which will give you a chance to face the Demiurge in the Real Side, where you can win a bonus if you manage to beat him.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Earn the favor of the Demiurge by mercilessly destroying your opponents in Competitive mode, or try your luck tricking a deity in Co-op. For those days when you feel omnipotent, you can take the lonely road to face the demiurge in Single Player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Many paths, only one option. Escape from the planet.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Meet the other side and find the truth.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
